content: Hello! That's an interesting droodle. How's your day going? Anything fun or inspiring happen?

I actually want you to tell me what you can see in the droodle.
It looks like two stick figures peeking over a horizon or perhaps something else entirely. What does it remind you of?
Ummm... I don't know a chicken?
I see what you mean! It could resemble a chicken's feet sticking up. How could we turn this into a little story? Maybe the chicken is having an upside-down adventure underground!

Hello! I’m your AI guide for building a doodle caption. I’m designed to ask you questions and guide your reasoning but if you want to take control of your own creative process, I’ll be happy to help wherever possible.
